WEBVTT

00:10:25.208 --> 00:10:30.809
It can commandeer HIV's machinery
to make more copies of itself,

00:10:30.833 --> 00:10:32.893
the amputated instruction set,

00:10:32.917 --> 00:10:38.268
and then each of these copies
can steal all of HIV's other components

00:10:38.292 --> 00:10:42.768
so that the cell gets converted
from a factory that produces virus

00:10:42.792 --> 00:10:45.684
to a factory that produces therapy.

00:10:45.708 --> 00:10:47.684
Hijackers.

00:10:47.708 --> 00:10:49.893
These carry no disease.

00:10:49.917 --> 00:10:52.726
This dramatically lowers HIV levels

00:10:52.750 --> 00:10:54.250
and keeps the cell healthier.

00:10:56.833 --> 00:11:00.643
This idea consumed me for months.